author: Matthew Impelli
title: Cruise Ship With 4 Dead Passengers and at Least 2 Coronavirus Cases Hoping to Dock in Florida
description: Holland America Line could not say if the deceased individuals were among the positive tests or if any of the four had the virus.
content:
Cruise line company Holland America Line confirmed Friday that four passengers died on its ship during a voyage, though the causes of death are unknown.
